  • Method Details

    • save

      public Printer save(String model, String description, String campusName, String buildingName, String roomNumber, boolean active) throws org.springframework.dao.DuplicateKeyException, Exception
      Saves a printer to the database.
      Parameters:
      model - the model of the printer
      description - a description of the printer
      campusName - the name of the campus where the printer is located
      buildingName - the name of the building where the printer is located
      roomNumber - the room number where the printer is located
      active - whether the printer is active or not
      Returns:
      the saved printer
      Throws:
      Exception - if the printer cannot be saved
      org.springframework.dao.DuplicateKeyException

      public void activatePrinter(String id) throws org.springframework.data.crossstore.ChangeSetPersister.NotFoundException, Exception

      Parameters:

      Throws:

      Exception - if an error occurs while activating the printer

    • deactivatePrinter

      Parameters:
      id - the id of the printer to deactivate
      Throws:
      org.springframework.data.crossstore.ChangeSetPersister.NotFoundException - if the printer with the given id cannot be found
      Exception - if an error occurs while deactivating the printer

      Updates a printer with the given id in the database.
      Parameters:
      id - the id of the printer to update

      campusName - the name of the campus where the printer is located
      buildingName - the name of the building where the printer is located
      roomNumber - the room number where the printer is located
      active - whether the printer is active or not
      Throws:
      NameNotFoundException - if the printer with the given id cannot be found
